{
  "texts": [
    "This enables the model to learn features, like edges and corners and textures that are quite small, but very important in learning patterns contained in an image.",
    "The convolutional procedure serves to pinpoint these low-level patterns.",
    "These patterns are combined in a progressive way to learned higher-level patterns in the layers of the network that are deeper.",
    "In this part of the model, the projection after activation of the input layer applies the relu activation function (Eq. 2).",
    "It will simply remove the effect of neurons with negative activations in the feature map rather than their positive counterparts."
  ]
}